nodes.text: If you're after concealment my favorite and regular carry is the Kel-Tec .380. Fits in the watch pocket of a pair of Levis, feeds six hollow points flawlessly and weighs almost nothing. Several of our deputy sheriffs carry them as summer off-duty pieces, which is how I discovered the convenience.
That is a nice little pistol with lots of smack for only 11 onces. Also, I like DA automatics.
